\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Essentially they come out and say \'93you\'92re average, but you\'92ve been with Jesus\'94 and that changes everything.\
