\cf4 \super 18\'a0
\f3\b0 \nosupersub Then they called them in again and commanded them not to speak or teach at all in the name of Jesus.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is the culture we live in today  (need to sit here longer)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Where we athletes can talk about whatever they want except Jesus.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We live in a culture that is free to express itself in anyway unless it is about Christianity.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Rap artist who can write offensive and dehumanizing lyrics about women and others and that is ok but don\'92t tell people you are a Christian that is offensive\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Happy Holidays but not Merry Christmas\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Athletes can praise themselves and become popular even for doing so but don\'92t tell people you\'92re a Christian like Tim Tebow on TV\'85no one wants to hear that.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We live in a culture that in many ways can\'92t deny some of the miracles and things have happened in Jesus name, but they are telling us not talk about Jesus.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f2\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Be a great person\'85don\'92t tell us why though\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \super 19\'a0
\f3\b0 \nosupersub But Peter and John replied, \'93Which is right in God\'92s eyes: to listen to you, or to him?\'a0You be the judges!\

\f2\b \super 20\'a0
